and demonstrate it isn't the club as much as it is

00:25.394 --> 00:29.219
the ball. But there have been some definite 
improvements on it. I think your clubs come out

00:32.263 --> 00:35.427
more the same. There is much more of a demand and a 
stress on having very high quality as far as not

00:35.548 --> 00:45.781
being deviating a lot. And that's helped a lot in 
consistency. But the

00:48.084 --> 00:54.473
main thing actually is just

00:58.638 --> 01:21.670
