they're off in the summertime or holidays, and the

00:58.638 --> 01:21.670
instruction at these schools, and the 
instruction level with PGA professionals has

00:58.638 --> 01:21.670
just really improved. You can become a better 
player with the help of these people who really

01:21.690 --> 01:23.312
